---
title: Karahi-Inspired Curry Chicken with Golden Tomato-Pepper Gravy and Spinach Rice
description: This recipe of tender chicken simmered in a gentle tomato curry broth is inspired by the flavours of karahi curries. It gets amped up by the bright, tangy and unexpected hit of roasted red pepper pesto.
